description.text:
Ever wonder if your iPhone think's it's smarter than you are? Use this charging station and remove all doubt.
While working on my trilogy of chargers, getting the measurements to work, I create a little test brick, something that'll print faster than a full throne. When I got it right I was left with a test brick (included) and I thought &quot;I could do something with this.&quot;
The iThrone <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:18725" >http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:18725</a> , iThrone Deluxe <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:18887" >http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:18887</a> , and IArmchair <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:19025" >http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:19025</a> have all been updated to these dimensions. In other words they are now based on real iPhone dimensions, not best guesses.
